Yeah so you don't have the body correct, here's how it should look:
```{
  "inputs": [
    {
      "properties": {
        "domain": "<http://testcompany1of5.com|testcompany1of5.com>",
        "name": "TestCompany1of5"
      }
    },
    {
      "properties": {
        "domain": "<http://testcompany2of5.com|testcompany2of5.com>",
        "name": "TestCompany2of5"
      }
    }
  ]
}```

